data.description: Beautiful waterfront home with views of the Olympic Mountains, Dyes Inlet, and awesome sunsets.  This 3 bedroom 2.5 bath home boasts Brazilian Cherry floors, gourmet kitchen with Cherry Cabinets, a great room with gas fireplace and Cherry wood built-ins, and oversize bedrooms. Primary bedroom has a spacious California Closet system and a 5 piece bathroom.  There is a gas tankless hot water system, a 1 year old furnace, a boat ramp, and a mooring buoy. Property includes two lots. Home is on the water-view lot while unimproved lot is waterfront with lower taxes. Lot dimensions and tax info include both lots.  Come celebrate sunsets every night and make this home yours
